author: Laura McKnight, NOLA.com | The Times-Picayune
title: 'Don't bring a gun to the parade route:' DJ Jubilee raps against Carnival-time violence, Fox 8 reports
text: The rapper, born Jerome Temple, said he's making a public plea for Carnival crowds to avoid settling disputes along parade routes, the news station reports.
